lead_paragraph: Napoli do not need Paris St Germain striker Edinson Cavani to return to the club as it would be difficult to bring him back into the team, their President Aurelio De Laurentiis said.

headline.print_headline: Napoli Do Not Need Cavani to Come Back, Says President
